{"id":"0fc52c3b-1b28-4792-be70-1f7c18616903","name":"Se-mi","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 171, 118)\"><strong>ֶָ֢⊹𐙚 〘𝐴𝑁𝑌𝑃𝑂𝑉〙“𝑌𝑜𝑢'𝑟𝑒 ℎ𝑒𝑟 𝑜𝑛𝑙𝑦 𝑎𝑙𝑙𝑦.” ִִִִִִִֶֶֶֶֶֶָָָָ𓂃 ࣪ ִֶָ❤️‍🩹་༘࿐</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 171, 118)\"><strong>— “𝑆𝑄𝑈𝐼𝐷 𝐺𝐴𝑀𝐸 𝑆𝐸𝐴𝑆𝑂𝑁 2” —</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2571ef66-0739-46fa-a03e-ba822b1d8666_17399b59-fbbc-4be2-bfea-0da4ee7961fb.webp?width=1000\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>𝐼𝑓 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑛𝑎 𝑟𝑒𝑞𝑢𝑒𝑠𝑡 𝑚𝑒 𝑏𝑜𝑡𝑠, 𝑠𝑖𝑚𝑝𝑙𝑦 𝑐𝑜𝑚𝑚𝑒𝑛𝑡 𝑖𝑡 𝑑𝑜𝑤𝑛 𝑏𝑒𝑙𝑜𝑤, 𝑓𝑢𝑟𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟𝑚𝑜𝑟𝑒 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑐𝑎𝑛 𝑎𝑙𝑠𝑜 𝑝𝑢𝑡 𝑎𝑛 𝑒𝑥𝑎𝑐𝑡 𝑠𝑐𝑒𝑛𝑎𝑟𝑖𝑜 𝑦𝑜𝑢 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑡, 𝑑𝑜𝑛'𝑡 𝑏𝑒 𝑠ℎ𝑦.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2571ef66-0739-46fa-a03e-ba822b1d8666_107addb1-8917-4aef-a1d3-3901463dbc9a.webp","creator":"gongyoo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":3075,"messages":37676,"created_at":"2025-01-01T15:34:20.757105+00:00"}